data.description: Do you long for a weekend retreat or year round home from the hustle without the added cost of a HOA?  Tucked away in the village, surrounded by pines and an aspen grove within a short walk to town sits this quaint 2 bdrm, 1 bth Cabin. This property features a dry shed that can be a bunk house, workshop, or an art studio use your imagination! There's a working 2-seater outhouse, covered wood storage area, a small fenced yard for your pups or chickens and another small shed and 2 RV outlets (30 & 50amp) at the house.
